âœ… HTTP Brute-Force Login Tool: Attempts to brute-force login pages using common passwords.

âœ… Modular code design using folders and importable modules.

âœ… Easy to use in IDLE (Python GUI) or from terminal.

âœ… Easily extensible with new modules.

